{"_id":"f13df3aa036dd66b","name":"El Tejido de Yomi · Nombres Verdaderos","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"flags":{"ocho-lanzas":{"tejidoSlug":"table-nombres","tejidoDataVersion":"1.0.0","tejidoFolderKey":"tables"}},"_stats":{"systemId":"ocho-lanzas","systemVersion":"0.3.14","coreVersion":"13.351","createdTime":1773500222224,"modifiedTime":1773500222224,"lastModifiedBy":""},"description":"<p>Escoge o lanza cuando Shizuku logre identificar la forma en que el bakemono se nombra a sí mismo.</p>","formula":"1d4","replacement":true,"displayRoll":true,"results":[{"_id":"97d22eb2245d4e26","type":0,"text":"Kumo-no-Yomi — Araña de Yomi","weight":1,"range":[1,1],"drawn":false,"img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","documentCollection":"","textColor":"","flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"ocho-lanzas","systemVersion":"0.3.14","coreVersion":"13.351","createdTime":1773500222224,"modifiedTime":1773500222224,"lastModifiedBy":""}},{"_id":"084ada23074ccac6","type":0,"text":"Itokami — El que teje el aliento","weight":1,"range":[2,2],"drawn":false,"img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","documentCollection":"","textColor":"","flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"ocho-lanzas","systemVersion":"0.3.14","coreVersion":"13.351","createdTime":1773500222224,"modifiedTime":1773500222224,"lastModifiedBy":""}},{"_id":"aae50aa295af9855","type":0,"text":"Kurohoshi-no-Tsuchi — Tierra de la estrella negra","weight":1,"range":[3,3],"drawn":false,"img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","documentCollection":"","textColor":"","flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"ocho-lanzas","systemVersion":"0.3.14","coreVersion":"13.351","createdTime":1773500222224,"modifiedTime":1773500222224,"lastModifiedBy":""}},{"_id":"fb17b5eb287c10fc","type":0,"text":"Amanohari — El hilo que desciende del cielo vacío","weight":1,"range":[4,4],"drawn":false,"img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","documentCollection":"","textColor":"","flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"ocho-lanzas","systemVersion":"0.3.14","coreVersion":"13.35