{"_id":"f3aaccb1ee8911e4","name":"El Tejido de Yomi · Complicaciones","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"flags":{"ocho-lanzas":{"tejidoSlug":"table-complicaciones","tejidoDataVersion":"1.0.0","tejidoFolderKey":"tables"}},"_stats":{"systemId":"ocho-lanzas","systemVersion":"0.3.14","coreVersion":"13.351","createdTime":1773500222224,"modifiedTime":1773500222224,"lastModifiedBy":""},"description":"<p>Úsala cuando la sesión pierda ritmo o quieras tensar el avance del tapiz.</p>","formula":"1d6","replacement":true,"displayRoll":true,"results":[{"_id":"6a2a4201fb867f4f","type":0,"text":"Un Kaibyō aparece junto a uno de los personajes, mirando fijamente hacia la casa de Okiya. Si lo siguen, descubren una nueva pista.","weight":1,"range":[1,1],"drawn":false,"img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","documentCollection":"","textColor":"","flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"ocho-lanzas","systemVersion":"0.3.14","coreVersion":"13.351","createdTime":1773500222224,"modifiedTime":1773500222224,"lastModifiedBy":""}},{"_id":"e34be1f83aecfce0","type":0,"text":"Kenji desaparece de casa de Jiro. Sus huellas van hacia la casa de Okiya y la marca de su palma ha crecido.","weight":1,"range":[2,2],"drawn":false,"img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","documentCollection":"","textColor":"","flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"ocho-lanzas","systemVersion":"0.3.14","coreVersion":"13.351","createdTime":1773500222224,"modifiedTime":1773500222224,"lastModifiedBy":""}},{"_id":"3260f0a2cc810e2d","type":0,"text":"Tanaka Sōsuke murmura en su sueño el nombre verdadero del Tsuchigumo. Solo hay unos segundos para entenderlo.","weight":1,"range":[3,3],"drawn":false,"img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","documentCollection":"","textColor":"","flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"ocho-lanzas","systemVersion":"0.3.14","coreVersion":"13.351","createdTime":1773500222224,"modifiedTime":1773500222224,"lastModifiedBy":""}},{"_id":"bc634df66f5bb6c0","type":0,"text":"Los hilos negros del exterior empiezan a contraerse. El avance del tapiz aumenta +2.","weight":1,"range":[4,4],"drawn":false,"img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","documentCollection":"","textColor":"","flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"ocho-lanzas","systemVersion":"0.3.14","coreVersion":"13.351","createdTime":1773500222224,"modifiedTime":1773500222224,"lastModifiedBy":""}},{"_id":"71cde3189bad0a94","type":0,"text":"La luz de la casa de Okiya se apaga por completo durante un minuto. El Tsuchigumo actúa desde la oscuridad.","weight":1,"range":[5,5],"drawn":false,"img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","documentCollection":"","textColor":"","flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"ocho-lanzas","systemVersion":"0.3.14","coreVersion":"13.351","createdTime":1773500222224,"modifiedTime":1773500222224,"lastModifiedBy":""}},{"_id":"987e87c7cd0d1242","type":0,"text":"Jiro llega corriendo: Okiya está diciendo en voz alta el nombre del personaje con mayor Maldición.","weight":1,"range":[6,6],"drawn":false,"img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","documentCollection":"","textColor":"","flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"ocho-lanzas","systemVersion":"0.3.14","coreVersion":"13.351","createdTime":1773500222224,"modifiedTime":1773500222224,"lastModifiedBy":""}}]}
